{"jobSummary": "Apple is where imaginations gather together, committing to the values that lead to great work. Every product we build, service we develop, or Apple Store experience we deliver is the result of us making each other’s ideas stronger. That happens because every one of us shares a belief that we can make something wonderful and share it with the world, changing lives for the better. It’s the diversity of our people and their thinking that encourages the innovation that runs through everything we do. When we bring everybody in, we can do the best work of our lives. Here, you’ll do more than join something — you’ll add something.

We are looking for a talented expert and innovation-driven team member to manage key international marketing programmes for our first party apps businesses, with a focus on offers for an 11 month fixed term position. The best candidate should demonstrate outstanding skills managing complex internal partnerships, strong attention to detail, be resourceful, adaptable, creative, and results-oriented. 
